    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Predicted relative hemolysis indices are consistently below the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five flow-speed combinations, with maximum prediction error of 8.7% relative to experimental benchmark data. The assessment is accepted for regulatory submission.",
